554
01:06:56,800 --> 01:06:59,155
MAN: What the fuck you doing?

555
01:07:22,920 --> 01:07:28,552
MAN: I'm coming home!
Laddie, I'm coming home!

556
01:07:29,000 --> 01:07:30,274
(MEN SINGING)

557
01:07:31,360 --> 01:07:37,515
Fuck 'em all! Fuck 'em all!
The long and the short and the tall

558
01:07:37,600 --> 01:07:42,230
Fuck all the Sergeants and WO1s
Fuck all the corporals

559
01:07:42,320 --> 01:07:43,799
