588
01:11:32,880 --> 01:11:36,873
-It's close to here.
-We're there. This is it.

589
01:11:58,600 --> 01:12:01,068
Here we are, guv. Down here.

590
01:12:36,320 --> 01:12:38,914
That's all right, guv. That's right.

591
01:12:40,880 --> 01:12:45,237
Get your head down. Get your head down.
There you go.

592
01:12:48,480 --> 01:12:49,833
(HUMMING)

593
01:13:00,080 --> 01:13:02,913
Tuck yourself in. Keep yourself warm.

594
01:13:09,760 --> 01:13:14,311
Chew on a bit of this. But quiet like,
or they'll all be wanting some.

595
01:13:17,800 --> 01:13:19,791
Try and get some sleep.

596
01:14:39,360 --> 01:14:41,510
(SINGING)

597
01:14:48,000 --> 01:14:49,069
ROBBIE: Find you.

598
01:14:50,360 --> 01:14:51,554
Love you.

599
01:14:52,320 --> 01:14:53,753
Marry you.

600
01:14:54,560 --> 01:14:56,357
And live without shame.

601
01:15:25,680 --> 01:15:31,312
I love you. Come back. Come back to me.

602
01:15:37,240 --> 01:15:39,310
-NETTLE: Bit too much noise, guv'nor.
-What?

603
01:15:41,400 --> 01:15:43,755
-What noise?
-You keep shouting.

604
01:15:43,840 --> 01:15:46,638
-Some of the lads are getting a bit peeved.
-What?

605
01:15:47,120 --> 01:15:48,997
(NETTLE SHUSHING)

606
01:15:58,280 --> 01:16:02,751
-Christ. You look a bit rough.
-Thing is, I've decided to stay on for a bit.

607
01:16:03,840 --> 01:16:06,991
I'm meeting someone,
and I'm always keeping her waiting.

608
01:16:07,080 --> 01:16:10,516
Now, listen. Listen to me, guv'nor.

609
01:16:11,120 --> 01:16:15,193
I went out for a Jimmy Riddle just now.
Guess what I saw!

610
01:16:15,760 --> 01:16:18,832
They're getting themselves sorted out
down on the beach.

611
01:16:19,120 --> 01:16:23,716
The boats are back, and a geezer from
the Buffs is marching us down at 7:00.

612
01:16:24,640 --> 01:16:27,837
We're away. We're off home, mate.

613
01:16:30,240 --> 01:16:33,869
So get some more sleep, and no more
of your bleeding shouting.

614
01:16:33,960 --> 01:16:37,999
-All right?
-I won't say a word.

615
01:16:40,720 --> 01:16:43,439
Wake me before 7:00, would you?
Thanks so much.

616
01:16:45,720 --> 01:16:50,510
You won't hear another word
from me. Promise.

