You know who you are.

620
01:17:44,080 --> 01:17:46,310
Which of you were responsible
for putting away the blankets today?

621
01:17:46,400 --> 01:17:48,356
-FIONA: I was, Sister.
-I don't suppose you can tell us

622
01:17:48,440 --> 01:17:49,839
-what you did wrong?
-No, Sister.

623
01:17:49,920 --> 01:17:51,638
Labels are folded to the inside,
are they not?

624
01:17:51,720 --> 01:17:53,073
-Yes, Sister.
-Do them again.

625
01:17:53,160 --> 01:17:57,312
Nurse Tallis, I'll see you in my office.
The rest of you are excused.

626
01:18:09,720 --> 01:18:12,757
-ls this job at all important to you, Tallis?
-Very important, Sister.

627
01:18:12,840 --> 01:18:14,956
Yesterday, you were seconded
to men's surgical.

628
01:18:15,040 --> 01:18:17,918
When your patient came round from his
anaesthetic, it seems the first thing he did

629
01:18:18,000 --> 01:18:20,355
was to ask for Briony.
Who might Briony be?

630
01:18:20,440 --> 01:18:23,477
-Well, me, Sister.
-There is no Briony.

631
01:18:23,560 --> 01:18:26,870
You are Tallis. Nurse Tallis.
Is that understood?

632
01:18:26,960 --> 01:18:28,075
Yes, Sister.

633
01:18:37,800 --> 01:18:39,233
