644
01:19:29,760 --> 01:19:31,478
There, you're done.

645
01:19:35,800 --> 01:19:36,835
Bother!

646
01:19:43,040 --> 01:19:44,029
Night-night, Ponty.

647
01:19:45,400 --> 01:19:47,118
Good night, Tallis.

648
01:20:01,800 --> 01:20:04,030
Don't panic! It's only me.

649
01:20:04,120 --> 01:20:07,669
Fiona, I almost jumped out of my skin.

650
01:20:08,440 --> 01:20:11,318
So this is where you duck to after lights out.

651
01:20:11,400 --> 01:20:15,439
I thought you might be in the middle
of some tempestuous romance.

652
01:20:15,800 --> 01:20:18,394
Don't you freeze to death up here?

653
01:20:20,720 --> 01:20:22,278
I love London.

654
01:20:23,920 --> 01:20:26,195
Do you think all of this will be
bombed and just disappear?

655
01:20:26,280 --> 01:20:27,315
No.

656
01:20:28,880 --> 01:20:30,393
I don't know.

657
01:20:31,280 --> 01:20:33,475
Do you write about Sister Drummond?

658
01:20:34,320 --> 01:20:36,550
-Do you write about me?
-Sometimes.

659
01:20:37,720 --> 01:20:41,076
-Can I look?
-I'd rather you didn't. It's private.

660
01:20:41,880 --> 01:20:45,350
I don't see any point in writing a story
if you're not going to let anyone read it.

661
01:20:45,440 --> 01:20:47,795
-It's not ready yet. It's unfinished.
