I am only now beginning to grasp.

690
01:22:46,920 --> 01:22:49,753
Cee, please write and tell me we can meet.

691
01:22:51,440 --> 01:22:53,192
Your sister, Briony.

692
01:22:55,440 --> 01:22:58,193
-FIONA: So do you?
-Do I what?

693
01:22:58,600 --> 01:23:02,718
Have a secret fianc in France.
