694
01:23:02,800 --> 01:23:03,789
No, of course not.

695
01:23:03,880 --> 01:23:06,348
Imagine not knowing if he'd ever come back.

696
01:23:06,440 --> 01:23:08,510
I've never been in love.

697
01:23:09,240 --> 01:23:11,834
